          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Well I am new to pune and out of experiences of my relatives and society PPL I got to know about this school , I like the environment of school, teaching staff and the number of activities they take each day . It's not about ONLY learning ABCD and blahh blaahh but they also help teaching and learning each and every things and manners which kids needs to learn  nowadays from school when their parents are busy in their working schedule. I personally admire Mr Ravi pawar sir . He helped me understand things which I wasn't aware in school. Thanks a ton .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
