          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sanika Gawade"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-21",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This was best school. Being a parent of class 10 student, in 2022-23 I saw there is no importance given to academics they have recruited one teacher who is not even a graduate and b.ed. I had an horrible experience of that same faculty. Always asking children to his class and calling himself Gunda of radcliffe.he is  maths teacher and  telling all his life stories and ruining the future of children. How can a school keep this kind of faculties I do not understand. Do not take admission here.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
