            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have been working in Radcliffe school since 10 months .I have learnt a lot of new things as a teacher .activity based learning is a key part of the school because of this method students can learn the subject thoroughly. Good environment for students .",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
