          "datePublished": "2023-02-12",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's a very good school, my kid is also studying in the same school since 3 years. All curriculum activities as well as sports activities are well conducted. Only the problem with the continuous changing in teaching staff. Kids are getting confused with the new teachers when they were totally comfortable with the existing teachers.. School has taken lots of new activities in school this year.. hope all kids get chance to show their active participation and show their talent in teams of curriculum, sports and cultural activities. All the very best!!!",
          "publisher": {
